37:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":"We aim to provide the Service on a 24×7 basis and target a monthly uptime of 99.5% excluding scheduled maintenance and events beyond our reasonable control. Support is provided via in-app chat and email during business hours (IST). Nothing in these Terms guarantees uninterrupted or error-free operation."}]
